					<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[
local camera = workspace.CurrentCamera
local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")
local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local sound = script.music

local cameraparts = game.Workspace.CameraParts

local cam1 = cameraparts:WaitForChild("Cam1")
local cam2 = cameraparts:WaitForChild("Cam2")
local cam3 = cameraparts:WaitForChild("Cam3")
local cam4 = cameraparts:WaitForChild("Cam4")
local cam5a = cameraparts:WaitForChild("Cam5")



local Successfulresetbutton = false


repeat wait() until camera.CameraSubject ~= nil 

game.StarterGui:SetCoreGuiEnabled(Enum.CoreGuiType.Backpack, false)

while not Successfulresetbutton do
	local WasSuccess, WContento = pcall(function()
		game.StarterGui:SetCore("ResetButtonCallback", false)
	end)

	if WasSuccess then
		Successfulresetbutton = true
	end
	task.wait()
end




camera.CameraType = "Scriptable"

camera.CFrame = cam1.CFrame

local fade = script.Parent.Parent.fade

local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
	3,
	Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
	Enum.EasingDirection.In,
	0,
	true,
	0

)

local fadegoal = {
	BackgroundTransparency = 0

}

local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

playfade:Play()


local cam1tocam2 = TweenInfo.new(
	3,
	Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
	Enum.EasingDirection.In,
	0,
	false,
	0
)


local cam1tocam2info = {
	CFrame = cam2.CFrame

}

local playtween = tweenservice:Create(camera, cam1tocam2, cam1tocam2info)

sound:Play()

playtween:Play()



local text1 = script.Parent.Parent.text1

local texttween = TweenInfo.new(
	4,
	Enum.EasingStyle.Bounce,
	Enum.EasingDirection.In,
	0,
	true,
	0

)

local textgoal = {
	TextTransparency = 0

}

local playtexttween = tweenservice:Create(text1, texttween, textgoal)

local cam2tocam3 = TweenInfo.new(
	4,
	Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
	Enum.EasingDirection.In,
	0,
	false,
	0

)

local cam2tocam3info = {
	CFrame = cam3.CFrame

}

local playtween2 = tweenservice:Create(camera, cam2tocam3, cam2tocam3info)

wait(3)

playtexttween:Play()

wait(5)

playtween2:Play()

wait(4)




playfade:Play()

wait(2.7)

script.Parent.Parent.helpbutton.Visible = true
script.Parent.Parent.playbutton.Visible = true
script.Parent.Parent.title.Visible = true

camera.CFrame = cam5a.CFrame

local cam5tocam4 = TweenInfo.new(
	2,
	Enum.EasingStyle.Bounce,
	Enum.EasingDirection.In,
	0,
	false,
	0

)

local cam5tocam4goals = {
	CFrame = cam4.CFrame

}


local playcam5tocam4 = tweenservice:Create(camera, cam5tocam4, cam5tocam4goals)

wait(0.3)
playcam5tocam4:Play()]]></ProtectedString>

					<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")
local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local makeuienabledfalse = script.RemoteEvent

local camera = workspace.CurrentCamera

script.Parent.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
	local button = script.Parent.playtext
	
	local mouseentertween = TweenInfo.new(
		1,
		Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
		Enum.EasingDirection.In,
		0,
		false,
		0		
	)
	
	local goals = {
		TextColor3 = Color3.new(0.827451, 0, 0)
		
	}
	
	local playtween = tweenservice:Create(button, mouseentertween, goals)
	
	playtween:Play()
	
end)

script.Parent.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
	local button = script.Parent.playtext

	local mouseentertween = TweenInfo.new(
		1,
		Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
		Enum.EasingDirection.Out,
		0,
		false,
		0		
	)

	local goals = {
		TextColor3 = Color3.new(0, 0, 0)

	}

	local playtween2 = tweenservice:Create(button, mouseentertween, goals)
	
	playtween2:Play()
	
end)


script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == true then
		makeuienabledfalse:FireServer()
		game.StarterGui:SetCoreGuiEnabled(Enum.CoreGuiType.Backpack, true)
		
		local mainguisclone = game.Lighting.MainGUIS:Clone()

		mainguisclone.Parent = player.PlayerGui
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.updatesui.Enabled = true
		
		wait(0.5)
		
		camera.CameraType = "Custom"
		
		script.Parent.Parent:WaitForChild("introscripts")["."].music:Stop()
		
		script.Parent.Parent.introscripts["."]:Destroy()
		
	elseif player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false and script.check.Value == true then
		script.check.Value = false
		local fade2 = script.Parent.Parent.fade

		local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
			3,
			Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
			Enum.EasingDirection.In,
			0,
			true,
			0

		)


		local fadegoal = {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0

		}

		local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade2, fadetween, fadegoal)

		playfade:Play()
	
		wait(2.7)
		
		camera.CFrame = workspace.CameraParts.CustomizeCam.CFrame
		
		script.Parent.Visible = false
		script.Parent.Parent.helpbutton.Visible = false
		script.Parent.Parent.title.Visible = false
		
		script.Parent.Parent.customizeui.Visible = true
		
		
		script.Parent.Parent.introscripts["."].music:Stop()
		
		fade2.BackgroundTransparency = 1
		
		
		
		
	end
	
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

						<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")

local db = true

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if db == true then
		db = false
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.playbutton.ape.check.Value = true
		local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

		local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
			3,
			Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
			Enum.EasingDirection.In,
			0,
			true,
			0

		)


		local fadegoal = {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0

		}

		local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

		playfade:Play()

		wait(2.7)

		script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false

		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.helpbutton.Visible = true
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.playbutton.Visible = true
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.title.Visible = true
		
		wait(1)
		fade.BackgroundTransparency = 1
		
		db = true
		
	end
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")
local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer


local db = true


script.Parent.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
	
	local title = script.Parent.continue_Roundify_12px.title
	
	local newtween = TweenInfo.new(
		1,
		Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
		Enum.EasingDirection.In,
		0,
		false,
		0
		
	)
	
	local target = {
		TextColor3 = Color3.new(0.827451, 0, 0)
		
	}
	
	local playtween = tweenservice:Create(title, newtween, target)
	
	playtween:Play()
	
end)

script.Parent.MouseLeave:Connect(function()

	local title2 = script.Parent.continue_Roundify_12px.title

	local newtween = TweenInfo.new(
		1,
		Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
		Enum.EasingDirection.In,
		0,
		false,
		0

	)

	local target = {
		TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)

	}

	local playtween = tweenservice:Create(title2, newtween, target)

	playtween:Play()

end)

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value ~= "none" then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Female" and db == true then
			db = false
			local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

			local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
				3,
				Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
				Enum.EasingDirection.In,
				0,
				true,
				0

			)


			local fadegoal = {
				BackgroundTransparency = 0

			}

			local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

			playfade:Play()

			wait(2.7)
			script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false

			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.picknamefemale.Visible = true
			
			wait(2.7)
			
			fade.BackgroundTransparency = 1
			
		elseif player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" and db == true then
			db = false
			local fade2 = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

			local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
				3,
				Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
				Enum.EasingDirection.In,
				0,
				true,
				0

			)


			local fadegoal = {
				BackgroundTransparency = 0

			}

			local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade2, fadetween, fadegoal)

			playfade:Play()

			wait(2.7)
			script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false

			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.picknamemale.Visible = true
			
			wait(2.7)

			fade2.BackgroundTransparency = 1
			
			
		end
	
	
		
		
		
		
	end
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")
local db = true

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").firstname.Value ~= "Starter" and player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").lastname.Value ~= "Player" and db == true then
		db = false
		local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

		local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
			3,
			Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
			Enum.EasingDirection.In,
			0,
			true,
			0

		)


		local fadegoal = {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0

		}

		local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

		playfade:Play()

		wait(2.7)

		script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.pickoutfitmale.Visible = true

	end


end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")
db = true

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").firstname.Value ~= "Starter" and player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").lastname.Value ~= "Player" and db == true then
		db = false
		local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

		local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
			3,
			Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
			Enum.EasingDirection.In,
			0,
			true,
			0

		)


		local fadegoal = {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0

		}

		local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

		playfade:Play()
		
		wait(2.7)
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.pickoutfitfemale.Visible = true
		
	end
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

		local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
			2,
			Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
			Enum.EasingDirection.In,
			0,
			true,
			0

		)


		local fadegoal = {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0

		}

		local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

		playfade:Play()
		
		wait(1.7)
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.pickoutfit.Visible = true
		
	end
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local customizevalues = player:WaitForChild("customizevalues")
local event = script.savedata
local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")
local camera = workspace.CurrentCamera

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if customizevalues.faceid.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.hairid.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.firstname.Value ~= "Starter" and customizevalues.lastname.Value ~= "Player" and customizevalues.gender.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.bodycolor.Value ~= "Tan0" then
			game.StarterGui:SetCoreGuiEnabled(Enum.CoreGuiType.Backpack, true)
			event:FireServer()
			local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

			local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
				3,
				Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
				Enum.EasingDirection.In,
				0,
				true,
				0

			)


			local fadegoal = {
				BackgroundTransparency = 0

			}

			local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

			playfade:Play()
			
			wait(2.7)
			
			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Visible = false
			
			wait(1)
			
			local mainguisclone = game.Lighting.MainGUIS:Clone()

			
			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.Enabled = false
			
			
			wait(0.5)
			
			camera.CameraType = "Custom"
			
			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.introscripts["."]:Destroy()
			
			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.playbutton.ape.RemoteEvent:FireServer()

			
			script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.updatesui.Enabled = true
			
			mainguisclone.Parent = player.PlayerGui
			
		end
		
	end
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

									<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local event = script.Parent
local dsservice = game:GetService("DataStoreService")

local hairdata = dsservice:GetDataStore("hairdata3")
local shirtdata = dsservice:GetDataStore("shirtdata3")
local pantsdata = dsservice:GetDataStore("pantsdata3")

local lastname = dsservice:GetDataStore("lastname3")
local gender = dsservice:GetDataStore("gender3")
local bodycolor = dsservice:GetDataStore("bodycolor3")
local hasplayeddata = dsservice:GetDataStore("hasplayed3")


event.OnServerEvent:Connect(function(plr)
	if plr:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		plr.values.haveplayed.Value = true
		plr:WaitForChild("customizevalues").shirt.Value = "DefaultShirt"
		plr:WaitForChild("customizevalues").pants.Value = "DefaultPants"
		
		wait()
		
		facedata:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.faceid.Value)
		wait()
		hairdata:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.hairid.Value)
		wait()
		shirtdata:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.shirt.Value)
		wait()
		pantsdata:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.pants.Value)
		wait()
		firstname:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.firstname.Value)
		wait()
		lastname:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.lastname.Value)
		wait()
		gender:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.gender.Value)
		wait()
		bodycolor:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.customizevalues.bodycolor.Value)
		wait()
		hasplayeddata:SetAsync(plr.UserId, plr.values.haveplayed.Value)
		wait(2)
		plr:LoadCharacter()
		
		
		
		
	end
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head

			remote:FireServer()


		end
	end
end)

local faces = game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("tempclothes").faces
local remote = script.changeface

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Text]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head

			remote:FireServer()


		end
	end
end)

local faces = game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("tempclothes").faces
local remote = script.changeface

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Text]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head

			remote:FireServer()

		elseif player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Female" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Name]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head

			remote:FireServer()


		end
	end
end)

		
		

	
]]></ProtectedString>

	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false and customizevalues.faceid.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.hairid.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.gender.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.bodycolor.Value ~= "Tan0" then

		playfade:Play()
		
		wait(2.7)
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.finishedui.Visible = true
		
	end
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local event = script.ape

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			local bc = game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"]:WaitForChild("Body Colors")
			
			bc.HeadColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.LeftArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.LeftLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.RightArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.RightLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.TorsoColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			
			event:FireServer()
				
		elseif player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Female" then
			local bc = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"]:WaitForChild("Body Colors")

			bc.HeadColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.LeftArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.LeftLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.RightArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.RightLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)
			bc.TorsoColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(204, 142, 105)

			event:FireServer()
			
			
		end
	
		
	elseif player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == true then
		player:Kick("noob")
		
		
	end
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local event = script.ape

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			local bc = game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"]:WaitForChild("Body Colors")
			
			bc.HeadColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.LeftArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.LeftLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.RightArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.RightLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.TorsoColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			
			event:FireServer()
				
		elseif player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Female" then
			local bc = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"]:WaitForChild("Body Colors")
			
			bc.HeadColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.LeftArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.LeftLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.RightArmColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.RightLegColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)
			bc.TorsoColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(176, 130, 99)

			event:FireServer()
			
			
		end
	
		
	elseif player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == true then
		player:Kick("noob")
		
		
	end
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

								<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local faces = game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("tempclothes").faces
local remote = script.changeface

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Text]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head

			remote:FireServer()

		elseif player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Female" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Text]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head

			remote:FireServer()


		end
	end
end)

								<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local faces = game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("tempclothes").faces
local remote = script.changeface

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Text]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"].Head

			remote:FireServer()

		elseif player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Female" then
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head.face:Destroy()
			local clone = faces[script.Parent.Text]:Clone()

			clone.Name = "face"

			clone.Parent = game.Workspace[player.Name.."female"].Head

			remote:FireServer()


		end
	end
end)

								<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local remote = script.ape


script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false then
		if player:WaitForChild("customizevalues").gender.Value == "Male" then
			
			local temphair = game.ReplicatedStorage.tempclothes.hair
			local temphairclone = temphair[script.Parent.Name]:Clone()

			for i,v in pairs(game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"]:GetChildren()) do
				if v:IsA("Accessory") then
					v:Destroy()

				end

			end

			temphairclone.Name = script.Parent.Name

			
			wait(0.1)
			
			game.Workspace[player.Name.."male"]:WaitForChild("Humanoid"):AddAccessory(temphairclone)
			
			
			remote:FireServer()
			
			
		end
		
	elseif player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == true then
		player:Kick("noob lol")
		
		
	end
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>

							<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local customizevalues = player:WaitForChild("customizevalues")
local tweenservice = game:GetService("TweenService")

script.Parent.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
	if player:WaitForChild("values").haveplayed.Value == false and customizevalues.faceid.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.hairid.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.gender.Value ~= "none" and customizevalues.bodycolor.Value ~= "Tan0" then
		local fade = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.Parent.fade

		local fadetween = TweenInfo.new(
			3,
			Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,
			Enum.EasingDirection.In,
			0,
			true,
			0

		)


		local fadegoal = {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0

		}

		local playfade = tweenservice:Create(fade, fadetween, fadegoal)

		playfade:Play()
		
		wait(2.7)
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Visible = false
		
		script.Parent.Parent.Parent.finishedui.Visible = true
		
	end
	
	
end)]]></ProtectedString>
